Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:46.02,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}星星在呢喃著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.15,0:00:48.94,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}雖然害怕…但還是想！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.44,0:00:54.40,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}光是安穩度日 也太無趣了點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.57,0:00:59.16,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}真希望能改變些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:02.87,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}既然想要個契機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.04,0:01:04.54,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}那就飛奔出去吧 Boooon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.54,0:01:08.71,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}回憶在騷動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.71,0:01:14.30,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}我…好像認識你！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.68,0:01:18.43,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}不論是晴天雨天還是在下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.43,0:01:21.18,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}我都好想好想去見你
