Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.72,0:01:23.85,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}從明天到未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:26.73,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}是啊 時間 Nonstop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:32.53,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}先前煩惱的事情 通通都消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.69,0:01:38.41,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}來展開新的故事吧
